      "text": "Police say DNA evidence links Luis Benitez-Gonzalez of Mexico to the murders of two women in Texas.\n\n🔎These murdered took place six years apart, and investigators believe there may be more victims. \n\nICE lodged a detainer with the Dallas County Jail to ensure he is not released back into the public while he faces justice for the alleged murders. \n\n➡️Dallas officials honor ICE detainers, which keeps their community safer from criminal illegal aliens.",
